Revision history for RPi-EEPROM-AT24C32

1.00 UNREL
        - Removed broken, unused eeprom_write_block() XS export (never sent the
          address MSB and read past the end of its 2-byte buffer); single-byte
          writes go through eeprom_write()

0.01    2019-06-28
        - initial version released
        - ability to write/read single bytes

